    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的评论状态流转图。核心场景是：学生在LMS门户提交评论后，先进入待审核状态，经过审批后才能公开可见。另外，被拒绝的评论要能记录原因，最终删除的评论需要流转到课堂服务做归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我梳理一下：LMS门户创建评论进入Pending，Pending可以走向Approved、Rejected或Deleted。Approved之后也能删除，Rejected同样可删除，Deleted最终流向ClassroomService。Pending状态内部需要细化吗？比如是否涉及成绩同步？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "AwaitingModeration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending内部要拆一下。评论创建后先触发GradeSync，然后进入AwaitingModeration，审核人员通过LMS门户操作审批。这个子状态要表达清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Pending的子状态结构我画好了。现在看Approved分支：审核通过后评论对学生可见，但老师应该还能编辑更新，这个要体现循环吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Visible和Edited之间要能来回转。Visible状态下老师点编辑进入Edited，保存后又回到Visible。数据源是StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Rejected分支我这样设计：评论被拒绝后先Hidden，然后必须或可选地添加拒绝原因，最终带原因的记录要同步到ContentCDN做审计留存。这个流程对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍微调整一下，添加原因不是强制的，但一旦有原因就要同步到ContentCDN。另外四个主状态旁边都加上注释说明，方便运维同事快速理解。",
      "elements_involved": [
